Class AbstractVariableTimedLoopStartNodeModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.core.node.NodeModel
      • com.vernalis.knime.internal.flowcontrol.nodes.timedloops.abstrct.loopstart.AbstractTimedLoopStartNodeModel
        • com.vernalis.knime.internal.flowcontrol.nodes.timedloops.abstrct.loopstart.AbstractVariableTimedLoopStartNodeModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TimedLoopStart, org.knime.core.node.workflow.LoopStartNode, org.knime.core.node.workflow.LoopStartNodeTerminator, org.knime.core.node.workflow.ScopeStartNode

    public class AbstractVariableTimedLoopStartNodeModel
extends AbstractTimedLoopStartNodeModel

    This is the Abstract model implementation of AbstractVariableTimedLoopStartNodeModel, which should be subclassed for variable timed loop starts. This node provides additional methods for handling the variable loops.

    Subclasses should implement RunForTime or RunToTime.

    Author:
    "Stephen Roughley "
